Pack with me and my @monostravel Carry-On Pro and Metro Belt Bag, the perfect travel accessories that ensure easy, perfect planning. Ad

The Carry-On Pro is designed to fit in the overhead bin of almost any flight, anywhere in the world with features including Three interior pockets can fit a 16” laptop, tablets, or magazines, ultra-sturdy telescopic handle, TSA-Accepted lock, whisper-quiet wheels, vegan leather details, and all-premium materials.

The Metro Belt Bag Designed for daily travel, the Metro Belt Bag is compact, functional, and versatile. Perfect for keeping all your travel essentials safe & protected.
